Cate Bauer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cate_Bauer 0 Cate Bauer (born 27 August 1922 in London, England) is an English actress who is best known for voicing the character Perdita in the animated film One Hundred and One Dalmatians (1961). She also played Miss Hidwick in the series The Third Man in the episode "How To Buy A Country" (1959).
